{
  "stem": "19111.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] He saw me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He saw that he's losing me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What he was able to do for me was bring little, like, a-- one potato or something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was able to cut little slices.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was a, a, a stove, a metal stove there-- and hold it up against the side of it to cook it and feed me a-- little pieces of potato.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[SIGHS] This is-- people next to me on the left side died one day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the people on the right side died another day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "New people were brought in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was there approximately a week to 10 days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I have reached a climax where I was delirious.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I think I was out of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When I woke up, my father was standing there, breathing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And, and, in a-- sort of a roundabout way, he was sort of, like, talking to himself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] But I have passed the crisis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The fever has subsided.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I've come out of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And most people died right there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Somehow, I survived it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And when I survived it, I was-- they were able to take me out of there and put me back with my father in the-- in the-- where I came from from that barrack, from that particular building that I was in.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] after a few months over there, I have-- suddenly, I looked up one day, up in the sky.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw tiny, little specks of planes flying over, which I haven't seen before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, I said to my father, I says, what, what, what is this-- what it is?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let's see.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so every single day, there were planes coming, coming over.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
